g.text: Employment in regional Victoria changed by -0.8% since March 2020 and is the second lowest of any Australian regional area in March 2021
Source: ABS Labour Force, Detailed (monthly). Note: most recent data is for March 2021.Data smoothed using a 3 month rolling average.
